project for algorithmic trading in Java is: Market Data Simulator + Moving Average Strategy
    What it does
        Simulates stock prices.
        Calculates a moving average.
        Generates BUY/SELL signals.
    
Concepts Demonstrated
    Java classes
    Collections (Queue)
    Streaming market data simulation
    Trading strategy pattern
    Console-based server-side logic

This is a realistic beginner trading-system PoC because it mimics the core flow used in real platforms:

    Market Data -> Strategy -> Trading Signal